videos.description: Blake Gallagher recovers Ian Book's fumble to set up Northwestern in Notre Dame territory.
videos.headline: Irish fumble handoff on opening drive

videos.description: Dexter Williams runs up the middle for a 1-yard Irish touchdown.
videos.headline: Notre Dame strikes first with 1-yard TD

videos.description: Clayton Thorson connects with Bennett Skowronek across the middle who makes the one-handed play to move the chains.
videos.headline: Skowronek makes one-handed snag on Northwestern 4th down

videos.description: Clayton Thorson keeps it up the middle for a 1-yard Northwestern touchdown.
videos.headline: Northwestern gets on the board with 1-yard TD run

videos.description: Ian Book finds Miles Boykin in the end zone for a Notre Dame touchdown.
videos.headline: Book connects with Boykin for 20-yard TD

videos.description: Ian Book connects with Michael Young down the middle for a 47-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Notre Dame extends lead with 47-yard TD pass

videos.description: Clayton Thorson finds Riley Lees downfield for a 27-yard Northwestern touchdown.
videos.headline: Thorson connects with Lees for 27-yard TD

videos.description: Cameron Ruiz lays out to block the Notre Dame punt and set up Northwestern at the Irish 17-yard line.
videos.headline: Northwestern blocks punt deep in Notre Dame territory

videos.description: Clayton Thorson QB sneaks up the middle for a 1-yard touchdown, cutting the Northwestern deficit to 24-21.
videos.headline: Thorson keeps it for 1-yard TD

videos.description: Ian Book fakes the handoff and runs up the sideline for a 23-yard Notre Dame touchdown.
videos.headline: Book goes untouched for 23-yard TD

videos.description: Ian Book gives credit to the Notre Dame coaching staff for setting up plays to free up its playmakers.
videos.headline: Book credits great play calling for win against Northwestern

videos.description: Ian Book throws two touchdowns and runs for another to power Notre Dame to a 31-21 win over Northwestern.
